  <name>KMPlayer</name>
  <summary>Interface for MPlayer by KDE</summary>
  <description>
    <p>KMPlayer is a simple frontend for MPlayer/FFMpeg/Phonon.</p>
    <p>Some features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>play DVD/VCD movies (from file or url and from a video device)</li>
      <li>embed inside konqueror (movie is played inside konqueror)</li>
      <li>embed inside khtml (movie playback inside a html page)</li>
      <li>Movie recording using mencoder (part of the mplayer package)</li>
      <li>No video during recording, but you can always open a new window and play it</li>
      <li>Broadcasting, http streaming, using ffserver/ffmpeg</li>
      <li>For TV sources, you need v4lctl (part of the xawtv package)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
